sources.description:
Ebola Rex - An ebola infected T-Rex escapes from a science lab in downtown Los Angeles, destroying everything in its path. Residents of a local neighborhood and a renegade soldier band together to deal not only with the monster on the loose, but the deadly and highly contagious disease it carries. 
2021.  Stars: Mel Novak, Shawn C. Phillips, Mike Ferguson
